Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:05.09,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mini戰國basara2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.39,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.68,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.61,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長曾我部君和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:11.67,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.20,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:53.24,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力 強度 射程 都沒話說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.16,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞富岳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.93,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此物甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:08.34,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.11,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這個在天下揚名立萬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:14.48,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如此更好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:15.52,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.64,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:26.88,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是吾毛利之要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:34.32,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煞風景的船體 用大鳥居裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:39.43,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一尺巨炮則改成了主炮天陽之墜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:44.73,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾將它變成了更接近天下的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.68,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.55,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我的富岳弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.72,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別稱它富岳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:57.03,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾已為其取了一個配得上吾毛利的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.18,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是元就丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.77,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是漁船風格的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.74,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到吾毛利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.11,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄子丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.03,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒譜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.44,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不叫日輪丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.54,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫日輪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.81,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫日輪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.26,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.42,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.40,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的要塞 富岳二式！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.61,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.92,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾要這麼來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.65,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是吾之要塞 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.26,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄子增員版
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.48,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日輪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.15,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.85,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的要塞 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.73,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超富岳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.67,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之海！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.77,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吾便這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.11,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之要塞 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.87,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄子增員鳥居增設版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.79,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大日輪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.91,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 你家的棄子站都站不穩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.31,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究是棄子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:24.96,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.08,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.20,heti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.16,maoli,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:56.49,changzeng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 開什麼玩笑！